public class ImageTable
extends javax.swing.JTable
implements java.awt.event.MouseListener
The class ImageTable, which inherits JTable and implements mousePressed() method for adding images to the spatial model. This class is used in ImageExplorer. Date Created: Dec 7, 2015
Author:
Kaito Ii <ii@fun.bio.keio.ac.jp>, Akira Funahashi <funa@bio.keio.ac.jp>
